    },
    {
      "text": "The following shipments notes are used:\n* Likely cleared: Shipment SHIP-2026-0731: seed stock ready for export to Brazil. Lab reference marker on the paperwork is TP53.\n* Likely flagged: Shipment SHIP-2026-0900: seed stock ready for export to Germany. Lab reference marker on the paperwork is BRCA1.",
      "type": "text",
      "layout": {
        "row": "Row_1h31mub",
        "columns": null
      },
      "id": "Field_0j1vwd9"
    },
    {
      "text": "# ...or hand in your own data",
